decks.notes: This deck focuses on quickly deploying artifact creatures and equipping them with various artifacts to create a powerful aggressive board presence. The goal is to overwhelm the opponent with a combination of efficient creatures, powerful equipment, and disruptive spells. By utilizing cards like Moonsnare Prototype, Metalwork Colossus, and Portable Hole, the deck aims to quickly close out games by leveraging the synergy between artifacts and aggressive creatures. In addition, the deck includes cards like Witching Well and Glint-Nest Crane to provide card selection and card advantage to maintain pressure on the opponent.
